1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 35=

3
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,600
Find what you came for.

4
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,420
I'll keep watch here.

5
00:00:25,762 --> 00:00:26,323
Understood.

6
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:35,320
Follow me.

7
00:00:51,325 --> 00:00:54,712
(Token)

8
00:00:56,812 --> 00:00:59,450
(Token)

9
00:01:00,159 --> 00:01:01,439
Even if I arrest you,

10
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,039
Luo Shixun won't trust me.

11
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,760
I want him to doubt you.

12
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,640
The deaths of our fathers

13
00:01:06,959 --> 00:01:07,920
are far from simple.

14
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:08,799
I'm aware.

15
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,000
Anran has uncovered some clues.

16
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:13,719
That is why I will feign capture.

17
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,879
You must act like you were caught

18
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,000
during a prison break.

19
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:19,280
The Luo family

20
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,879
will think they've caught us both,

21
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,120
and they'll drop their guard.

22
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:24,959
Then, we can work from both sides
to gather the evidence.

23
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:25,640
But Chang,

24
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:27,120
I can't leave you in prison.

25
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,120
Don't worry.

26
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,319
My aunt will assist me.

27
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,359
I need just one day.

28
00:01:33,690 --> 00:01:35,439
I have to bring
all the evidence we've found

29
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,439
to someone.

30
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:38,200
Who?

31
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:41,920
His Majesty.

32
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,319
Are you...

33
00:01:50,439 --> 00:01:52,150
I am a Commander
of the Embroidered Guard.

34
00:01:52,510 --> 00:01:54,550
To investigate the Gate Bureau
and the Sacred Token,

35
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,959
I went undercover there
as a humble constable.

36
00:01:57,879 --> 00:01:58,560
Chang.

37
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,100
Your father was one of us.

38
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,840
My father?

39
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,840
So, that is our plan.

40
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,719
The Embroidered Guard found this.

41
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:28,560
The truth behind the deaths
of your father and Chu Xiangshan.

42
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,479
What are you doing?

43
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,080
I made a mistake.

44
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,800
I got Wuxia hurt.

45
00:02:46,475 --> 00:02:47,599
Please, don't kill me!

46
00:02:47,787 --> 00:02:48,599
I beg you, spare me!

47
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:50,240
Uncle, can't you make him be quiet?

48
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,319
Shut your mouth!

49
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:53,840
Chang,

50
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:55,639
what should we do next?

51
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,479
We fall back to the Big Buddha Temple.

52
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,240
Let's go.

53
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,639
Commissioner.

54
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:13,719
We've sealed off every road.

55
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:14,520
Chu Yunchang

56
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,599
is now cornered.

57
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:20,919
They've likely holed up
in the Big Buddha Temple.

58
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,560
They'll use the Vice Minister

59
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,240
as leverage.

60
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:25,080
Surround the temple. Now!

61
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:26,960
Sir,

62
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,199
if they use the Vice Minister against us,

63
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:32,520
how do you want us to handle it?

64
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,759
Just focus on the targets.

65
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,439
I'll deal with the fallout.

66
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:36,879
But...

67
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,000
Yes, sir.

68
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,560
Move out!

69
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,159
Grandfather.

70
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,650
About what Wuxia said...

71
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:52,290
Shuang.

72
00:03:53,225 --> 00:03:55,100
To achieve greatness,
one must make sacrifices.

73
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:56,560
Wuxia is dead

74
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:58,199
because of Chu Yunchang.

75
00:03:58,199 --> 00:04:00,080
She will pay for his life in blood.

76
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:02,319
I understand.

77
00:04:04,975 --> 00:04:09,000
(Meditation Hall)

78
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:14,599
(Meditation Hall)

79
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:15,520
Chu Yunchang!

80
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:19,319
You're surrounded. There's no way out!

81
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,240
Release the Vice Minister immediately.

82
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,040
Do it,

83
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:26,000
and I might let you live.

84
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:27,800
Otherwise, we all go down together.

85
00:04:37,125 --> 00:04:37,764
Light it up.

86
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:46,519
Chang.

87
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,000
They're going to burn the place down.

88
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:51,160
We have no choice.
We have to negotiate.

89
00:04:55,512 --> 00:04:59,800
(Meditation Hall)

90
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,920
Kill me,

91
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:03,439
and the Vice Minister dies with me.

92
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,240
What are your terms?

93
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:11,560
I want you.

94
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:15,120
Come in alone and we'll talk.

95
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,480
Grandfather!

96
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:19,040
Don't worry, Shuang.

97
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:20,759
Fine.

98
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:22,600
I'll go in alone

99
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:23,920
and negotiate with you.

100
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,879
Tell your men

101
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,959
to stay back.

102
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,040
No one moves

103
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,800
without my order!

104
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,720
Satisfied?

105
00:05:37,050 --> 00:05:38,500
(Meditation Hall)

106
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,279
Save me! Help!

107
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:47,000
Commissioner Luo, save me!

108
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,759
Forgive the delay, sir.

109
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:53,439
I've entered alone as you asked.

110
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:55,120
Now, release Vice Minister Zhou at once.

111
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:57,160
Let him go?

112
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:59,199
And become sitting ducks for you?

113
00:05:59,199 --> 00:06:00,600
If you release him,

114
00:06:00,759 --> 00:06:02,480
I will stay behind as your hostage.

115
00:06:03,759 --> 00:06:05,319
We don't trust a word you say.

116
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,959
Stalling like this

117
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,279
will only end badly for you.

118
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:10,262
I am the Commissioner
of the Gate Bureau.

119
00:06:10,262 --> 00:06:11,240
My word is my bond.

120
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:13,160
Release the Vice Minister,

121
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,279
and I'll guarantee your safe passage.

122
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:15,800
Deal?

123
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:19,879
Is that the same lie
you told my grandfather

124
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:21,000
and Dongfang Qing?

125
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:27,680
Do you have a better plan?

126
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,279
Fine.

127
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:30,680
Then let me tell you this.

128
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:33,120
The Vice Minister has been poisoned.

129
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,759
If you let us leave safely,

130
00:06:34,759 --> 00:06:36,279
we'll release him.

131
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:37,879
I'll give you the antidote.

132
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,240
If you break your word,

133
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:43,199
he's going down with us.

134
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,079
Thorough as always.

135
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,600
Deal.

136
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,360
Let him go.

137
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,360
Help me...

138
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:09,720
Get me out of here!

139
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:10,600
Vice Minister.

140
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,000
You're safe.

141
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:13,600
Take me

142
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:14,839
back to my manor.

143
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:15,879
You there!

144
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:17,639
Escort the Vice Minister home.

145
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:18,238
Yes, sir!

146
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,959
The Vice Minister is safe now.

147
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,219
Withdrawn your men.

148
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:30,079
Withdraw?

149
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:36,720
I should have let Dongfang Qing
finish you off years ago.

150
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:38,959
Today, I'm sending you
to join him in the grave.

151
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:51,839
Luo Shixun!

152
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,600
You gave your word!

153
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,820
You're a fool for believing me.

154
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,800
Chang! Chang!

155
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,240
Chang!

156
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,120
Luo!

157
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,319
Don't you want the antidote?

158
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,520
You're just going to
let the Vice Minister die?

159
00:08:17,090 --> 00:08:18,480
You're the ones who poisoned him.

160
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,240
How is it my responsibility?

161
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,360
If that fool dies,

162
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:26,079
I'll just use your corpses
to prove I "avenged" him.

163
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,560
By then,

164
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,240
I'm sure the Vice Minister will rest

165
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,360
very peacefully.

166
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,639
You're as twisted as they come.

167
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,720
Was that

168
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:39,039
how you played my grandfather?

169
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,679
What if it is?

170
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:43,720
So you admit it.

171
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:47,159
I orchestrated Chu Zhongtian's death.

172
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,759
I stole the Sacred Token.

173
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:53,759
I turned him
and Dongfang Qing against each other.

174
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,679
It was all me.

175
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:58,480
I branded the Sacred Hand Sect as a cult.

176
00:08:58,810 --> 00:09:00,159
I put you on the most-wanted list.

177
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:02,519
It was my plan from the start.

178
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:04,120
I've admitted it. Now what?

179
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:07,000
My grandfather trusted you with his life.

180
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,679
How could you do it?

181
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,919
Because he was a fool.

182
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,759
I am an officer of the law.

183
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:13,919
And he was a thief.

184
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:16,039
I am the Commissioner of the Gate Bureau.

185
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:18,390
Why would I ever lower myself
to be friends with a criminal?

186
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,519
Then, you shouldn't have befriended him.

187
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,399
Why must you frame him?

188
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,519
Because the Sacred Hand Sect

189
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:25,440
had no right to exist.

190
00:09:25,759 --> 00:09:27,399
Who does the Chu family think they are?

191
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,399
Trying to control
the Martial World and lead the alliance?

192
00:09:30,890 --> 00:09:32,519
You have no respect for the Gate Bureau.

193
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,919
If everyone listens to you,

194
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,720
where is the Imperial Court's authority?

195
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:40,120
So you set this all in motion

196
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,080
to tear the Martial World apart.

197
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,799
To feed your own ego,

198
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:45,279
you framed innocent people

199
00:09:46,159 --> 00:09:47,960
and murdered Dongfang Qing
to keep him quiet.

200
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,440
He thought knowing my little secret

201
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,440
gave him leverage over me.

202
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:59,240
I've spent years
manipulating the Martial World.

203
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:02,679
Chaos out in the Martial World
is chaos for the folks!

204
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:04,679
By wiping out your sect

205
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,879
single-handedly,

206
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,759
the Court will finally see
the Gate Bureau's value.

207
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:10,840
Then,

208
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:15,600
I'll toss the Sacred Token
back into the world.

209
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:19,559
Imagine the bloodbath that will follow.

210
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,879
The Court will have to rely on us.

211
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:27,360
And the Embroidered Guard
and Eastern Bureau

212
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:31,360
will never dare look down on me again.

213
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:36,360
Wuxia was a good man.

214
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:40,159
All he wanted was to find
a way out for your family.

215
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:41,799
And yet,

216
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,480
you were busy
doing these shameful things.

217
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:46,279
You're the reason we have no heir.

218
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:48,720
Today,

219
00:10:49,679 --> 00:10:51,879
I'll kill you to avenge Wuxia.

220
00:10:51,987 --> 00:10:53,468
Aren't you afraid of retribution?

221
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,240
Retribution?

222
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:58,559
That official believes
whatever I tell him.

223
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,790
Once I've killed you both,

224
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,519
nobody will know the truth.

225
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:02,960
There is no retribution.

226
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:08,480
Take a good look at who's behind you.

227
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,399
Vice Minister Zhou!

228
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:38,159
That's enough. The town is just ahead.

229
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,350
No need to escort me further.

230
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,159
You can all head back.

231
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:40,919
Yes, sir.

232
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:42,600
But before you go,
I have a gift for you.

233
00:11:51,679 --> 00:11:54,279
Wait, didn't the Vice Minister leave?

234
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:55,519
Ms. Luo!

235
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,960
The Commissioner might be in trouble.

236
00:11:58,679 --> 00:11:59,320
Get in there!

237
00:11:59,320 --> 00:11:59,990
Stop right there!

238
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,000
Mao Wenrong,
by what right do you give orders?

239
00:12:08,010 --> 00:12:10,490
By the right that your grandfather
is harboring the Sacred Token!

240
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:13,519
Where is your proof?

241
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:15,519
The evidence is already in Yu's hands.

242
00:12:15,679 --> 00:12:16,919
He's inside that hall right now.

243
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:21,360
Constable Yue,
this case isn't what it seems.

244
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,639
Don't do anything rash.

245
00:12:26,279 --> 00:12:27,519
Is this a mutiny?

246
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:29,679
You'd just leave
the Commissioner in danger?

247
00:12:29,799 --> 00:12:30,879
You traitors!

248
00:12:31,020 --> 00:12:32,390
Black-Clad Secret Guards, hear me!

249
00:12:32,559 --> 00:12:33,159
Seize them!

250
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,200
Constable Yue!

251
00:12:36,279 --> 00:12:37,399
We are officers of the law.

252
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:38,639
If we can't find the truth

253
00:12:38,639 --> 00:12:39,679
and punish the guilty,

254
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:41,300
how can we justify
the uniform we wear?

255
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,399
Nobody move!

256
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,290
We wait for orders from the top.

257
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:46,279
Yue Lun!

258
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,799
My grandfather is the Commissioner.

259
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,600
Who could possibly outrank him?

260
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:53,919
Behold the Imperial Tablet
of the Northern Constabulary!

261
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,279
(Commander of the Northern Constabulary Office)
Mao Buyu is on the Emperor's orders.

262
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:56,720
He has the authority to kill
before a trial.

263
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,679
Who dares defy him?

264
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,039
Will you defy the decree?

265
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:03,559
I've never seen that tablet before.

266
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,150
I only take orders from my Commissioner.

267
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:06,519
Black-Clad Secret Guards!

268
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,840
Stand down!

269
00:13:08,020 --> 00:13:09,840
Drop your weapons
or face a charge of treason!

270
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,679
Form up!

271
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:11,399
- Yes!
- Yes!

272
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:24,159
Luo Shixun.

273
00:13:24,679 --> 00:13:27,360
So all these years
of chaos in the Martial World

274
00:13:27,759 --> 00:13:29,919
was your doing.

275
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:31,200
Vice Minister!

276
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,720
Please, let me explain.

277
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,399
What more is there to explain?

278
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,879
You were ready to have me murdered!

279
00:13:42,799 --> 00:13:44,879
This is all a plot by the Chu family!

280
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:45,720
Vice Minister,

281
00:13:45,879 --> 00:13:47,080
we serve the same Court.

282
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:49,919
Don't listen to the lies
of these common thieves.

283
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:51,200
Besides,

284
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,639
I don't even have the Sacred Token.

285
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,200
Liar!

286
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:59,080
Mao Buyu, Commander
of the Embroidered Guard.

287
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,990
His Majesty ordered me
to investigate the Sacred Token.

288
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:08,840
Vice Minister.

289
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:11,080
(Token)
We found this Sacred Token

290
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,240
hidden in Luo Shixun's study.

291
00:14:13,462 --> 00:14:17,262
(Token)

292
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:21,000
You're with the Embroidered Guard?

293
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,039
Yes.

294
00:14:25,925 --> 00:14:29,200
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

295
00:14:29,238 --> 00:14:32,113
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

296
00:14:32,613 --> 00:14:38,331
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

297
00:14:39,513 --> 00:14:42,833
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

298
00:14:42,963 --> 00:14:45,883
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

299
00:14:47,051 --> 00:14:52,291
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

300
00:14:53,513 --> 00:14:55,906
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

301
00:14:55,906 --> 00:14:59,556
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

302
00:14:59,625 --> 00:15:03,115
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

303
00:15:03,213 --> 00:15:06,188
♪To the ends of time♪

304
00:15:06,188 --> 00:15:09,563
♪The moon traces your face♪

305
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:13,338
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

306
00:15:13,338 --> 00:15:19,578
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

307
00:15:19,913 --> 00:15:23,128
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

308
00:15:23,413 --> 00:15:26,951
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

309
00:15:27,238 --> 00:15:30,263
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

310
00:15:30,263 --> 00:15:33,363
♪On our way to forever♪

311
00:15:33,363 --> 00:15:37,213
♪The moon traces your face♪

312
00:15:37,213 --> 00:15:40,573
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

313
00:15:40,763 --> 00:15:46,723
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

314
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:57,440
♪Just to be with you♪
